description: Creates a service, which defines the configuration for the following entities:   Up to three records (A, AAAA, and SRV) or one CNAME record   Optionally, a health check   After you create the service, you can submit a RegisterInstance request, and Amazon Route 53 uses the values in the configuration to create the specified entities. For the current limit on the number of instances that you can register using the same namespace and using the same service, see Limits on Auto Naming in the Route 53 Developer Guide.
